1). Add the dependency on gradle (app level)
2). Apply Plugin for hilt
3). Add permission for Internet
4). Create Package for mainapp and Create MainApp.kt and set main app to manifest file in application tag
5). Create Package for name network constant and create a file NetworkConstant
6). Create Model call for response
7). Create netoworkCall package nad Create ApiService Class and add BASE_URL and some other url
8). Create NetworkModule and write code for retrofit call
9). Create Repository package and create DataRepository class
10). Create a repository module